OL,3,CDriver who led police on chase which
OL,4,Ckilled mother-of-three sentenced
OL,6,FA van driver who hit and killed a
OL,7,Fwoman on a golf course in
OL,8,FStaffordshire has been sentenced.
OL,10,FJohn McDonald, 51, drove his Nissan
OL,11,Fvan into Aston Wood Golf Club during a
OL,12,Fpolice chase last April and ran into
OL,13,FSuzanne Cherry, who had been playing
OL,14,Fgolf with her husband.
OL,16,FThe court heard how he stepped over
OL,17,Fthe body of Suzanne before fleeing the
OL,18,Fscene.
