OL,3,CDriver who led police on chase which
OL,4,Ckilled mother-of-three sentenced
OL,6,FJohn McDonald was sentenced to 13
OL,7,Fyears and six months for death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and conspiracy to
OL,9,Fcommit fraud at Worcester Crown Court.
OL,11,FHe was also disqualified from driving
OL,12,Ffor 16 years and eight months.
OL,14,FJohnny McDonald, who was in the van
OL,15,Fwith McDonald was sentenced to two
OL,16,Fyears and six months for conspiracy to
OL,17,Fcommit fraud.
OL,19,FBrett Delaney who was also in the van
OL,20,Fwas sentenced to two years, three
OL,21,Fmonths for conspiracy to commit fraud.
