OL,3,CDriver who led police on chase which
OL,4,Ckilled mother-of-three sentenced
OL,6,FMcDonald had led police on a 12 minute
OL,7,Fchase through the streets of
OL,8,FBirmingham of speeds up to 70mph, the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FHe damaged vehicles, drove on the
OL,12,Fwrong side of the road, mounted
OL,13,Fpavements and rammed a police car at
OL,14,Fleast 12 times.
OL,16,FHe then turned into the golf course in
OL,17,FShenstone before hitting Ms Cherry,
OL,18,Fwho had been looking for her ball near
OL,19,Fa stream.
