OL,3,CDriver who led police on chase which
OL,4,Ckilled mother-of-three sentenced
OL,6,FHer husband Clint Harrison shouted her
OL,7,Fname to warn her the van was
OL,8,Fapproaching as it careered over an
OL,9,Fembankment, but she "could not
OL,10,Fpossibly have got out the way", the
OL,11,Fcourt was told.
OL,13,FShe suffered multiple catastrophic
OL,14,Finjuries and was taken to Queen's
OL,15,FElizabeth hospital. She died four days
OL,16,Flater, a day before her 63rd birthday.
