OL,3,CDriver who led police on chase which
OL,4,Ckilled mother-of-three sentenced
OL,6,FMr Harrison said his wife's life was
OL,7,F"violently and senselessly ended", as
OL,8,Fhe read his victim impact statement
OL,9,Fwhile looking directly at John
OL,10,FMcDonald in the dock.
OL,12,FHe said: "I stand before you today not
OL,13,Fas a man seeking vengeance, but as a
OL,14,Fman who had the very foundation of his
OL,15,Flife destroyed.
OL,17,F"Suzanne's life was violently and
OL,18,Fsenselessly ended by the actions of
OL,19,Fthis defendant.
