OL,3,CDriver who led police on chase which
OL,4,Ckilled mother-of-three sentenced
OL,6,F"This life was not abstract, it was
OL,7,Fthe life of the brightest and most
OL,8,Fbeautiful soul I ever met."
OL,10,FHe also said: "They valued their
OL,11,Ftemporary freedom more than her right
OL,12,Fto live. The damage is irreversible.
OL,14,F"We are condemned to a lifetime of
OL,15,Fgrief. They must be held fully
OL,16,Faccountable for dismantling our
OL,17,Ffamily."
OL,19,FMs Cherry's brother Adrian Cherry
OL,20,Fdescribed her as "tough and resilient".
