OL,6,FHe said: "Sue was the victim of such
OL,7,Fcruel events. One minute enjoying a
OL,8,Fgame of golf, the next ploughed down
OL,9,Fby a reckless act. My life will never
OL,10,Fbe the same.
OL,12,F"I remember her zest for life and
OL,13,Fadventure. She lost her life in what
OL,14,Fshould have been a safe place. To this
OL,15,Fday, I have no answers."
